  "detailed_description": "Once, you were a good and nice boy, like sunshine. Till that day, the misfortune befell you. Your favourite toy car crashed into that tree, at the gate of the park.<br />\r\nThe lost precious tought you to hate. You hate all trees in the world.<br />\r\nSo here you are, the legendary Lumber King.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClick to cut off all the trees;<br />\r\nLead your heroes and let them cut off all the trees;<br />\r\nCollect roots, levelup your heroes, cut off more trees;<br />\r\nCollect Wood Souls, levelup your skills, cut off more trees;<br />\r\nUse you power to evolve your hero, make them stronger, cut off more trees;<br />\r\nFinally, this world will be a desert;<br />\r\nYou really hate green.",
